At Odyssey Studios, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, 
and how we keep it secure. By using our services, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.

Understanding
"Hardware ID" an amount of numbers specifically for a device or system
"IP Address" an amount of numbers or characters specifically
When you hear we, that is refering to Odyssey, The Developer(s)

The Data we collect

A. Hardware ID
Your Hardware ID is collected to identify your device and to ensure the proper functioning of the game.

B. IP Address
Your IP address is collected to help us identify and prevent any fraudulent activity.

Why or what we use this data for
We use the given information for the following purposes:

To provide and improve our services, such as by personalizing content and recommendations.
To communicate with users, such as by sending updates and promotional emails.
To analyze usage data and improve our services.
To comply with legal obligations, such as responding to requests from government authorities.
To prevent fraudulent activity by identifying and blocking suspicious IP addresses.
How we clear/delete your collected data
You may contact us at any time to request that we delete your data and remove your account from our server.

Getting In Contact With us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at arvinkho@outlook.com.
